INSERT INTO build_request (
                id,
                request_type_id,
                object_address,
                track_id,
                status,
                version_code,
                owner_version,
                created_at
            )
            
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
            
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                status = EXCLUDED.status
